&lt;ul class=&quot;ul1&quot;&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li4&quot;&gt;5+ years of experience in database or systems infrastructure engineering, with hands-on expertise in Nutanix, SQL Server, and PostgreSQL administration.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li4&quot;&gt;Proficiency in PowerShell scripting for Windows automation and Python scripting for infrastructure automation, data processing, and ETL pipeline development.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li4&quot;&gt;Experience designing and maintaining ETL pipelines across heterogeneous database and file-based sources, including error handling, retry logic, and scheduling.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li4&quot;&gt;Strong working knowledge of Linux system administration (RHEL/AlmaLinux/Rocky Linux 9.x or Ubuntu 22.04/24.04 LTS) and Windows Server 2019 system administration, including storage layout, networking, OS hardening, and lifecycle management.&lt;/li&gt;
