&lt;p&gt;Looking for a motivated electronics design engineer to design the next generation of boards for all of Lunar Energy’s products!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An ideal candidate is enthusiastic, eager to learn and ready to collaborate with a dedicated, cross-functional team to create innovative, best-in-class products starting with home energy storage systems. Engineers at Lunar are hands-on, comfortable with both simulation and real hardware, and able to carry product development from the concept stage through high-volume production.&lt;/p&gt;
