&lt;li&gt;Design and develop digital electronics, analog electronics, and small power supplies for various components of our home energy system.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborative work with mechanical, firmware, EMC, RF, design validation, thermal design, compliance, reliability, and manufacturing test engineers.&lt;/li&gt;
